sequenceDiagram
    actor Admin
    participant View as Anggota Index
    participant Controller as AnggotaController
    participant Model as Anggota Model
    participant DB as Database

    Admin->>View: Klik Menu Anggota
    View->>Controller: GET /admin/anggota
    Controller->>Model: Anggota::all()
    Model->>DB: Select * From anggotas
    DB-->>Model: Return Collection
    Model-->>Controller: Return Data
    Controller-->>View: Render Tabel Anggota

    Admin->>View: Klik Tambah Anggota
    View->>Controller: GET /admin/anggota/create
    Controller-->>View: Tampilkan Form Create

    Admin->>View: Submit Data Anggota
    View->>Controller: POST /admin/anggota
    Controller->>Model: Anggota::create(data)
    Model->>DB: Insert into anggotas
    DB-->>Model: Return Created ID
    Controller-->>View: Redirect with Success
